### 14. KEY SYNCHRONIZATION MECHANISMS

| Lock/Mechanism | Purpose | Location |
|----------------|---------|----------|
| `db.cmtx` (Mutex) | Ensures compactions & deletions don't run simultaneously | Held during entire `Compact()` |
| `db.autoCompactMtx` | Protects `autoCompact` flag from concurrent changes | `db.run()` |
| `db.mtx` (RWMutex) | Protects block list and general layout | Brief read for plan/compact, write for reload |
| `db.compactc` (chan) | Non-blocking signal to trigger compaction | Appender.Commit() sends, db.run() listens |
| `db.compactCancel` | Cancel context for running compactor | Set at DB init, used if shutdown initiated |

